               <p>
            
               
                  <persName id="t16880113-21-defend101" type="defendantName">
                     Richard 
                     Connel
                  <interp inst="t16880113-21-defend101" type="surname" value="Connel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-21-defend101" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-21-defend101" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , an Irish-man, of <placeName id="t16880113-21-defloc98">St. Margarets Westminster</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t16880113-21-defloc98" type="placeName" value="St. Margarets Westminster"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t16880113-21-defloc98" type="type" value="defendantHome"></interp>
                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880113-21-defend101 t16880113-21-defloc98"></join>, was Indicted for <rs id="t16880113-21-off99" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16880113-21-off99" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-21-off99" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a Silver Tankard, value 5 l. from 
                     
                        <persName id="t16880113-21-victim103" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Tipler
                        <interp inst="t16880113-21-victim103" type="surname" value="Tipler"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t16880113-21-victim103" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t16880113-21-victim103" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880113-21-off99 t16880113-21-victim103"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  
               
                  </rs>, on the <rs id="t16880113-21-cd100" type="crimeDate">2d. of January</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880113-21-off99 t16880113-21-cd100"></join> last. It appeared that he came into this Tipler's House, and called for a Tankard of Drink, he carried off the Tankard; and being afterward taken, he confessed it to the Constable, and did not deny is in the Court: Upon which he was brought in <rs id="t16880113-21-verdict101" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16880113-21-verdict101" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               guilty
            </rs>.</p>
